flowchart TD
    U[User question + database] --> API[Request validation]
    API --> RET[Schema and value retrieval]
    DB[(Read-only database)] --> RET
    RET --> PROMPT[M-Schema prompt assembly]
    PROMPT --> MODEL[Qwen3-4B + project QLoRA adapter]
    MODEL --> PARSE[SQL extraction + sqlglot parse]
    PARSE --> SAFE{Single read-only query?}
    SAFE -->|No| ERROR[Safe error / bounded correction]
    SAFE -->|Yes| EXEC[Immutable SQLite execution]
    DB --> EXEC
    EXEC -->|Failure| ERROR
    EXEC -->|Success| RESULT[Rows + SQL + metadata]
    RESULT --> SUMMARY[Deterministic or model summary]
    RESULT --> CHART[Rule-based chart selection]
    SUMMARY --> OUT[Transparent answer]
    CHART --> OUT
    OUT --> U

